dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Ronald Murphy. May I have your name, please?
Thank you, Donna. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's zero three two zero five seven.
Thank you. Can you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle for verification purposes?
Of course, it's a two zero one seven Toyota Corolla.
Great, thank you for verifying that information, Donna. Is there anything specific you'd like assistance with today regarding your policy?
I just wanted to inquire about updating my contact information.
Certainly, I can assist you with that. Please provide me with the updated address and phone number.
My new address is five five Maple Street, and my new phone number is nine eight seven six five four three two.
Perfect. Thank you for updating your information, Donna. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out to us. Have a great day!
